This block is a simple alternative to Cinder's TextLayout
and TextureFont. It behaves more like a text field in 
Flash, etc. It supports automatic word wrapping, and dynamic
changing of text, fonts, and leading. It extends ci::Area, 
allowing for quick resizing, collision detection, etc.

